===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|ja|やおい|tr=yaoi|sc=Jpan}}, an acronym of '''''ya'''ma nashi, '''o'''chi nashi, '''i'''mi nashi'' ({{l|ja|[[ヤマ]][[なし]]、[[オチ]][[なし]]、[[意味]][[なし]]}}), "no climax, no point, no meaning".
